channel.title: Umm, I have no clue what to do
channel.description:
Hi,
I'm very new to Moparscape, I haven't even downloaded it. I want to download a Moparscape that is not the real RuneScape, and that I won't get IP banned from RuneScape. When I have downloaded Moparscape, can I just open it, type in something in the login-thingy and then log in to RuneScape and get the items I want with just a click..?
Please answer, or post a link to a guide... :rolleyes:
-Sasuke :cool:

item.dc:creator: @Rictoo Rictoo
item.description:
@Rictoo wrote:

Sasuke -

If you are talking about moparscape Revolution (the client that connects to the normal Runescape)
then this:

Moparscape Revolution is just the normal runescape, except with a few addons, like zooming, moving the camera... etc

Now there is another Moparscape for private servers (run by people like you, and me)
Private servers have nothing to do with the normal Runescape

I hope I answered your question
